[## [SECTION: Common Errors and Fixes — Phases 4 & 5]]

278
02:27:24,000 --> 02:27:30,000
Let me walk through common errors in Phases 4 and 5.
And how to fix them.

279
02:27:30,000 --> 02:27:36,000
Error one. AttributeError saying repo.create.
The cause is a duplicate write block still in routes.py.

280
02:27:36,000 --> 02:27:42,000
When you added the analysis history recording, you may have left a second block.
Remove the duplicate and keep only one call to repo.record.

281
02:27:42,000 --> 02:27:48,000
Error two. RuntimeError saying pgvector not found at startup.
The pgvector extension is missing from your database.

282
02:27:48,000 --> 02:27:54,000
The fix is to run CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS vector in psql.
Connect to your database and run that command.

283
02:27:54,000 --> 02:28:00,000
Error three. connect already called.
This means initialise_dependencies is calling connect twice.

284
02:28:00,000 --> 02:28:06,000
The cause is both your lifespan and something else calling connect.
Check your dependencies file and make sure connect is called only once.

285
02:28:06,000 --> 02:28:12,000
Error four. RateLimitExceeded in tests.
SlowAPI is counting test requests and hitting the rate limit.

286
02:28:12,000 --> 02:28:18,000
The fix is to use TestClient from FastAPI.
TestClient bypasses real rate limiting in the test environment.

287
02:28:18,000 --> 02:28:24,000
Error five. 401 Unauthorized on the health endpoint.
Your load balancer or test can't reach /health.

288
02:28:24,000 --> 02:28:30,000
The cause is that health path is not in the exempt paths list.
APIKeyMiddleware.EXEMPT_PATHS must include slash health.

289
02:28:30,000 --> 02:28:36,000
Error six. LLM_BASE_URL mismatch.
You have Groq URL set but you're using an OpenAI API key.

290
02:28:36,000 --> 02:28:42,000
Groq API keys start with gsk underscore.
OpenAI API keys start with sk dash project or sk dash.

291
02:28:42,000 --> 02:28:48,000
Match your key type to your base URL.
If using Groq, use a Groq key. If using OpenAI, use an OpenAI key.

292
02:28:48,000 --> 02:28:54,000
Error seven. max_tool_calls hit immediately on the first request.
The agent is calling tools but not getting results.

293
02:28:54,000 --> 02:29:00,000
The cause is that your LLM model does not support function calling.
Not all models support tools.

294
02:29:00,000 --> 02:29:06,000
For OpenAI, use gpt-3.5-turbo or newer.
For Groq, use llama3 or newer.

295
02:29:06,000 --> 02:29:12,000
Error eight. CORS error in your browser.
Your frontend cannot call the API because of cross-origin restrictions.

296
02:29:12,000 --> 02:29:18,000
The cause is that your frontend origin is not in CORS_ORIGINS.
CORS_ORIGINS controls which web domains can call your API.

297
02:29:18,000 --> 02:29:24,000
The fix is to add your frontend URL to CORS_ORIGINS in .env.
For example, comma-separated list of allowed domains.


